quran[15]{c,v,t}:
  69,38,Motero Ine ndilumbira pali chilichonse chimene uli nkuona
  69,39,Ndi chimene chili chobisika
  69,40,Kuti ndithudi awa ndi mawu a Mtumwi wolemekezeka
  69,41,Ndipo si mawu a Mlakatuli ayi ndipo chikhulupiriro chanu ndi chochepa
  69,42,"Ndipo si mawu a munthu wa maula ayi, ndipo ndi zochepa zimene inu mukumbukira"
  69,43,Ichi ndi chivumbulutso chochokera kwa Ambuye wa zolengedwa zonse
  69,44,Ndipo iye akanapeka nkhani yokhudza Ife
  69,45,Ndithudi Ife tikadagwira dzanja lake lamanja
  69,46,"Ndipo, ndithudi, Ifetikadadulamtsemphawakewamoyo"
  69,47,"Ndipo palibe, wina wa inu, amene akadatiletsa Ife kumugwira"
  69,48,"Ndipo, ndithudi, Korani iyi ndi chikumbutso kwa iwo amene amapewa zoipa"
  69,49,"Ndipo, ndithudi, Ife timadziwa kuti alipo ena a inu amene amaikana"
  69,50,"Ndipo, ndithudi, ilo lidzakhala lomvetsa chisoni kwa anthu osakhulupirira"
  69,51,"Ndipo, ndithudi, ichi ndi choonadi chokhachokha"
  69,52,"Motero lemekeza dzina la Ambuye wako, Wamkulu kulu"